# 🔹 GROUP 5 — Growth / monotonicity

These protect your **core graph guarantees**

---

## 12. Monotonic node growth

### T

Add events

### R

Nodes never disappear

---

## 13. Monotonic edge growth

### T

Add edges over time

### R

